{"tid":945669,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"凱滙買家Full pay 3房單位幫兒子上車　冼太：佢鍾意用就用！","createTime":"2018-12-18T05:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T12:21:28.000Z","uid":88097,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0ea10fcf4fd497147bceb94ba2eb7da38226f13b","tid":945669,"uid":88097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:19:08.000Z","msg":"信置（0083）等牽頭發展的觀塘凱滙第一期，今日次輪推售383伙。已為退休人士的頭籌客冼太買入3房中層單位供兒子上車，斥資過千萬元。「無諗住畀首期，我諗住一次過畀晒算囉，唔需要做按揭。」<br />\n<br />\n冼太本身住在九龍區，她透露，今年30歲以上的兒子尚未結婚，「買定畀佢，佢鐘意用就用，無所謂。」<br />\n<br />\n她又稱，兒子在觀塘區上班，該區交通方便、配套好，未來發展不錯。<br />\n<br />\n更多凱滙揀樓客心聲︰<br />\n<br />\n凱滙頭籌客黃太：擬購高層單位投資　明年樓雖價跌但會「升返！」<br />\n<br />\n凱滙傳沽200伙 選逾千萬兩房戶 曾太：幫女婿揀到「平價貨」<br />\n<br />\n【凱滙開售】買家李生：對觀塘區有感情 呎價3萬都會買<br />\n<br />\n凱滙明日次輪推售383伙 藝人陳煒、蘇頌輝到場參觀示位<br />\n<br />\n首輪未抽中  今次入四張飛<br />\n<br />\n上周首輪推售首批488伙「一Q清袋」，不少買家未能買入心儀單位，冼太上輪就抽到1,900號籤，「上次都有嚟，但諗住都入唔到，就冇再排隊入去囉，睇到個龍尾都唔到我囉，所以就行開囉。」今次她抽到2號籤，「今次入多咗票，入咗四張。」<br />\n<br />\n她對新盤相當滿意，「今次好好彩，多謝畀我揀到個心儀嘅單位」，「呢個樓盤係好有潛質，所以好有信心。」被問到樓市下跌，她稱：「跌極都有限啦，呢啲咁嘅筍盤。」<br />\n<br />\n凱滙發展商今輪推售的兩張價單，包括1至4房單位，當中第4張價單涉280伙，以最高折扣20.5%計，折實平均呎價18,488元。而第5張價單則涉103伙，折實平均呎價則為19,688元。合共推383伙。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/272395/%E5%87%B1%E6%BB%99%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6full-pay-3%E6%88%BF%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E5%B9%AB%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%8A%E8%BB%8A-%E5%86%BC%E5%A4%AA-%E4%BD%A2%E9%8D%BE%E6%84%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%B0%B1%E7%94%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%2F272395%2F%25E5%2587%25B1%25E6%25BB%2599%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E5%25AE%25B6full-pay-3%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D%25E5%25B9%25AB%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%2590%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E5%2586%25BC%25E5%25A4%25AA-%25E4%25BD%25A2%25E9%258D%25BE%25E6%2584%258F%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E7%2594%25A8&d=80JSO3C4DhQkSCqIxZi%2BV%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=78c36204\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/272395/%E5%87%B1%E6%BB%99%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6full-pay-3%E6%88%BF%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E5%B9%AB%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%8A%E8%BB%8A-%E5%86%BC%E5%A4%AA-%E4%BD%A2%E9%8D%BE%E6%84%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%B0%B1%E7%94%A8</a><br />\n<br />\n邊個話香港後生仔難上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d190f0e9965be121e48055b3bc8e6a3a859f4a1","tid":945669,"uid":24044,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:24:00.000Z","msg":"媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8ac57a0903cd5b0b6803e34d506e01d39c5489","tid":945669,"uid":2054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:25:13.000Z","msg":"買樓禁個制咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b223b5878b9dec3625ff6472b3a793385f7347f1","tid":945669,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:30:23.000Z","msg":"母幹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1bbf33e3e578a97f89f76c087a97789ce96271","tid":945669,"uid":43117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:33:55.000Z","msg":"一炮過<br />\n自住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68fabac619b0f1d070c0c00cce5bf159a207e922","tid":945669,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:42:19.000Z","msg":"媽咪呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1856f74d378e55ebe28b739b43f7a20049eccae","tid":945669,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:43:21.000Z","msg":"恭喜"},{"pid":"e87609ab40e736f26fd261a9e364f9fae47e3e11","tid":945669,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05: